    <div class="features">
      <div class="card reveal in"><span class="tag">01</span>
        <div class="icon"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8"></circle><path d="M12 1v3M12 20v3M1 12h3M20 12h3"></path></svg></div>
        <h3>Precision Farming</h3>
        <p>GPS-guided tractors, satellite imagery, and AI models analyze every square meter — applying exactly the right amount of seed, water, and nutrient where the plant needs it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal in"><span class="tag">02</span>
        <div class="icon"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 2C8 8 4 12 4 16a8 8 0 0016 0c0-4-4-8-8-14z"></path></svg></div>
        <h3>Smart Irrigation</h3>
        <p>Soil-moisture sensors and weather-aware controllers deliver water drop by drop — cutting consumption by up to 60% while boosting crop quality and root health.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal in"><span class="tag">03</span>
        <div class="icon"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 2l3 6 6 1-4.5 4.5L18 20l-6-3-6 3 1.5-6.5L3 9l6-1z"></path></svg></div>
        <h3>Agricultural Drones</h3>
        <p>Autonomous drones scan fields with multispectral cameras, spot diseases days before the human eye, and spray treatments with surgical accuracy.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal in"><span class="tag">04</span>
        <div class="icon"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="2"></circle><circle cx="18" cy="6" r="2"></circle><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="2"></circle><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="2"></circle><path d="M6 8v8M18 8v8M8 6h8M8 18h8"></path></svg></div>
        <h3>Biotechnology</h3>
        <p>Gene-editing and selective breeding create crops that resist drought, pests, and disease — producing nutrient-dense harvests on land once considered unfarmable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card reveal in"><span class="tag">05</span>
